info.author: Frank T. Bergmann
info.description: libSEDML is a library for reading, writing and manipulating SEDML.  It is written in ISO C and C++, supports SEDML Levels 1, Version 1-3, and runs on Linux, Microsoft Windows, and Apple MacOS X.  For more information about SEDML, please see http://sed-ml.org/.
